args.justification: This class covers privacy and rights over personal information specifically in technological/AI contexts, which aligns with a broader AI ethics grouping focused on privacy and transparency; assigning this shared Class_Group connects it to related transparency concerns.

This class addresses ethical dilemmas around transparency of AI decision-making, which is a core facet of AI ethics closely related to privacy and control over information; assigning the same Class_Group as the privacy rights class creates a coherent higher-level AI ethics cluster.
